Cheetor moved quietly around the mess hall and towards to where the 
sound had indicated from. "What's all the commotion?," he asked, 
glancing towards AzureBlade in his beast mode. He then turned to the 
stranger, before looking behind him.

"Ah did I miss something?" he eyed the stranger one last time. Who was 
this bot? He hadn't seen him around before... had he?

OMWOS
